# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# YÀN Atelier · .gitignore
# Last refactor: 2026-06-22 — bucketed by source after WeChat-Claude bridge
# session generated ~46 untracked files (mood refs / AI staging / WeChat raw
# / AutoEdit cache). Goal: ignore noise, keep real assets.
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
# Windows accidentally-created sentinel file
nul

# ─── Editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ─── Archives / secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.zip
.env
.env.*
secrets/
*.pem
*.key

# ─── AutoEdit cache (PNG conversion artifacts) ────────────────────────
# `_ensure_png()` in D:/YAN_AutoEdit converts .jpg→.png for gpt-image-2
# /edits upload. The .upload.png siblings are throwaway cache.
*.upload.png

# ─── WeChat raw message downloads (encrypted CDN URLs as filenames) ───
# Look like _cgi-bin_mmwebwx-bin_webwxgetmsgimg__&MsgID=...&skey=@crypt_...
# Direct WeChat web/desktop exports — no business in the repo. Replace
# with properly-named copies if any are keepers.
images/_cgi-bin*
images/_cgi*

# ─── AI generation staging (raw output — rename or delete before commit) ─
# AI gen tools dump `output (N).png` here. Rename to meaningful filename
# (e.g. images/mood-XYZ.png) if keeping, otherwise delete.
images/output.png
images/output (*).png
images/output_*.png

# ─── Ad-hoc numbered exports (WeChat dump / clipboard saves) ──────────
# Files like images/1.png, images/2.png, images/00 (N).png — rename
# meaningfully if keeping, otherwise let them gitignore-vanish.
images/[0-9].png
images/[0-9][0-9].png
images/[0-9][0-9][0-9].png
images/00 (*).png

# ─── Video assets (too large for git history) ─────────────────────────
# .mp4 files routinely 1-13MB. Use external storage (Cloudflare R2 /
# Google Drive / dedicated CDN) or commit only with explicit decision.
video/*.mp4
video/*.mov
video/*.webm
video/*.MOV

# ─── Local-only test artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────
test_output.txt
*.log
*.tmp
